<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-7AEE1ECC-C765-4F0F-8B5A-D9E3E00A767B" version="1" lang="en-US"?><concept xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-7AEE1ECC-C765-4F0F-8B5A-D9E3E00A767B" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic concept)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c concept oceConcept-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic concept/concept "><title class="- topic/title ">15 The drive of the Xtran unit</title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="GUID-34C6A3E5-E809-4139-80CC-275A8CCF9EDC"><p class="- topic/p ">The <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">X motion system drive motor</compname><compcodenr class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr " translate="no"> 15M1 </compcodenr><compsignal class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compsignal " translate="no">XMS_DRV_MO</compsignal></comp> drives, via 2 drive belts, the Xtran roller. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The speed of the motor is controlled by <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">X motion system drive motor encoder</compname><compcodenr class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr " translate="no"> 15B1 </compcodenr><compsignal class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compsignal " translate="no">XMS_DRV_MO_ENC</compsignal></comp>. The sensor is visible in black mounted on the end of the motor on the right. 
</p><fig class="- topic/fig " id="FIG_0EC308F66DEE42CEA15A116CC1CD2E08"><image class="- topic/image " href="GUID-5110B801-E4F7-4B20-93C7-D40D57B9AB27-low.png" id="IMAGE_1228EC14C5A2479CB8A52E36F337E80F" placement="inline" otherprops="GUID-5110B801-E4F7-4B20-93C7-D40D57B9AB27-low.png"/></fig><fig class="- topic/fig " id="FIG_D7FB6B4EC9F44CAA8C957E43899784C4"><image class="- topic/image " href="GUID-E677D772-E6CD-4BD8-A0ED-9B376F4C9248-low.png" id="IMAGE_8437817A65444AEE851C230CC06DCF95" placement="inline" otherprops="GUID-E677D772-E6CD-4BD8-A0ED-9B376F4C9248-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">The speed of the Xtran roller is checked by <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">X motion system drive roll encoder</compname><compcodenr class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr " translate="no"> 15B4 </compcodenr><compsignal class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compsignal " translate="no">XMS_DRV_ROL_ENC</compsignal></comp>. This sensor in gray is shown at the left hand side of the picture. 
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Functional description</category></metadata></prolog><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-56142F1B-D3A1-46E9-910C-EEE3067DB3E1.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Functional description</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
